@startuml
!pragma layout smetana
title Linear state machine (v2.2 · sync 2026-07-03) — 4 statuses + label signals\n(transition = trigger + model)

skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #EAF3FF
  BorderColor #336699
  FontName Helvetica
}

[*] --> Todo : PLAN push (idempotent)\nai:planned · type:* · estimate · blocked-by

Todo --> Todo : DEV asks @Mateusz\n(needs:answer / needs:approval, PL)
Todo --> InProgress : DEV pick (dor-ok, dep-aware, WIP=1)\n+ plan approved (emoji ✅) · 👀 + assignee @flow
Todo --> Canceled : dropped
InProgress --> InReview : deliver_task(): DoD check + actual_hours\n+ summary PL/EN · ai:coded · clears needs:*
InProgress --> InProgress : checkpoint -> STATE.md\nresume via .state/*-wip.json
InReview --> InProgress : changes requested\n(Conventional Comments · round++ · max 2 -> escalated)
InReview --> Done : review clean + tests pass\nai:reviewed + dod-ok
Done --> [*] : CADENCE digest (weekly)

state InReview {
  [*] --> Reviewing
  Reviewing --> Testing : approve -> assign VERSION\n(stage:testing)
  Testing --> [*] : deploy (health-check + rollback)\n+ synthetic tests pass
  Testing --> Reviewing : retest
}

note right of Todo
  Entry gate = dor-ok flag
  (Why/AC/scope-out/deps/type/estimate).
  XL estimate -> re-decompose.
  type:spike -> ADR, skips deploy.
end note

note right of InReview
  3 parallel passes: first-pass (DeepSeek V4 Pro)
  · security (Kimi K2.7) · deep (GLM-5.2, risk-tiered).
  Max 2 dev<->review rounds -> escalated.
  Testing = deploy GCP VM
  (health-check + auto-rollback, no prod PII).
end note

note bottom of InProgress
  Flags any state: needs:{answer|approval|decision|access}
  · blocked · risk:high · escalated · over-budget.
  Escalation ladder: retry -> Kimi/Opus -> needs:* + STOP.
  1 task = 1 commit · no git push without approval.
end note
@enduml
